  <bioghist id="aspace_0667d0433e4621a495b80b5a2f0a9b91">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Bates is Professor Emeritus, Plant Biology (Bailey Hortorium) and former Director of the L. H. Bailey Hortorium at Cornell University.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_7f6dc2a7cf18406031e596f61934a399">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes correspondence and reports about the hortorium and material on Conservation Farming in the Tropical Uplands (CFTU); Cornell International Institute for Food, Agriculture and Development (CIIFAD); the Organization for Tropical Studies and the Society for Economic Botany.</p>  </scopecontent>
